# ELMESACAD - Design System & Architecture Rules

## Graphic Charter
- Primary Color: #058AC5 (Main brand color)
- Secondary Color: #E76067 (Accents and CTA)
- Black: #272826 (Text and headings)
- Gray: #D4D6D3 (Borders and disabled states)
- White: #FFFFFF (Backgrounds)
- Green: #5ECB44 (Success states)

## UI Components Rules
- Buttons: Rounded corners (12px), elevation 2. Primary for main actions, White with Gray border for secondary.
- Inputs: OutlinedBorder, 1.5px thickness, color Gray, turns Primary on focus.
- Cards: White background, subtle shadow (blurRadius: 10, color: Black with 0.05 opacity), borderRadius: 16.
- Spacing: Use a 8px grid system (8, 16, 24, 32).

## Business Logic
- Credit System: Each page read (trigger: PageView change) MUST deduct 1.15 credits from `User.credits`.
- Navigation: Use GoRouter or AutoRoute for handling PUSH and TAB navigation separately.

## Architecture
- Folder structure: 
  - lib/core/theme (colors, typography)
  - lib/core/widgets (reusable components)
  - lib/features/[feature_name]/screens
  - lib/features/[feature_name]/providers (Riverpod or Provider)